column4: Hey can somebody please tell me how to fix the error "*** glibc detected *** double free or corruption (!prev): 0x081781d8 ***
Unable to read printer database." or is this a bug in Dapper that needs to be reported
double free means a bulk of memory has been freed and then try free it again ,usually causing by program's bug
then this is probably a glibc bug that needs to be reported
